of happiness...

1150
01:52:37,625 --> 01:52:40,458
our children. Of our own.

1151
01:52:42,125 --> 01:52:43,250
So...

1152
01:52:44,208 --> 01:52:47,208
thank you for loving me.

1153
01:52:55,291 --> 01:52:59,791
I saw this article...

1154
