1168
01:55:05,750 --> 01:55:08,125
I was in a concentration camp.

1169
01:55:14,416 --> 01:55:17,750
Alan. Go, uh, go put
on your swimming shorts.

1170
01:55:17,833 --> 01:55:19,541
- Have some fun.
